translate ru AfterEpilogueBlackMonolithWarrior_9c4bf3d4:
    # "Was he still out there?"
    ""

translate ru AfterEpilogueBlackMonolithWarrior_898eb0f5:
    # "She had no cause to know one way or another, and yet, one some level she could not imagine he wasn't still out there."
