translate ru AfterEpilogueBlackMonolithWarrior_2b8ba9bb:
    # "Each had walked away from the other, knowing that they weighed to heavily on the other."
    ""

translate ru AfterEpilogueBlackMonolithWarrior_89bef528:
    # "Had they stayed together, neither could ever have been free again of the other."
    ""

translate ru AfterEpilogueBlackMonolithWarrior_6bfb32e6:
    # "Then why, if she had severed the link to be free of him, did she find that he still lingered on her mind?"
