translate ru AfterEpilogueBlackMonolithWarrior_b7f3b205:
    # "But Sarah also knew the thought came when it wanted, not when she wanted it."
    ""

translate ru AfterEpilogueBlackMonolithWarrior_6ecffc3a:
    # "Her mind drifted in his direction, and she could only suffer it."
